"Jingva Testimonials (New)","settings":{"title":"Rock-solid Base","theme_mode":"light","show_subtitle":true,"description_font_size":18,"image_to_title_gap":48,"title_to_description_gap":12,"image_to_description_gap_no_title":24,"description_to_buttons_gap":24,"image_to_title_gap_mob":12,"title_to_description_gap_mob":48,"image_to_description_gap_no_title_mob":12,"description_to_buttons_gap_mob":24,"padding_top":160,"padding_bottom":0,"padding_top_mob":96,"padding_bottom_mob":96,"title_color":"#0a0a0a","bg_color":"#ffffff","bg_color_mob":"#ffffff"}},"jingva_how_it_works_9RpcpB":{"type":"jingva-how-it-works","name":"Jingva How It Works","settings":{"heading":"How it works","anchor_id":"how-it-works","image_pc":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/M6__PC.jpg","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/M6__MOB.jpg","video_url":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=PzNiPv2m04g"}},"testimonials_8jw3te":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_kw4GmX":{"type":"testimonial","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7_01_webp_759dc8b9-594b-4021-93fa-87cc4f944343.webp","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Jorena","content":"<p>Auoto M6 ultra  den krassesten Caming Stuhl den ich auf diesem Planeten jemals gesehen habe.ein riesen Paket und ich freue mich das mit euchzu Öffnen der Aufbau war so einfach dass auch Leute verstehen und ganz einfach zusammen schrauben konnten.dieser Stuhl sieht nicht nur gut aus nein der hat auch einfach eine Sitzheizung für den Winter und für den Sommer sogar eine Belüftungsfunktion.<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_8DateJ":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7_02_webp_c7a4122d-8779-4ef6-b2dd-21e6d3496524.webp","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Hall Of Tech","content":"<p>The autofull g7 ergonomic chair which was tested and approved by an actual chiropractor.So,yeah,my spine's about to live its best life.Just look at it.It has 22 adjustable features like auto lumber support.<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_UMkdX4":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7_03_webp_204eb2b6-48ed-4d17-baff-f9c144e98ff4.webp","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Frslush","content":"<p> My chair actually has heating 、cooling and messaging built in，whitch is crazy overkill, but I love it！<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_HTwJwH":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2025-10-20_162858_820_-_frame_at_0m2s_1.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Above average","content":"<p>The most high tech gaming chair on the market just got even crazier 👀<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_LKtazX":{"type":"testimonial","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/20251020-163310_-_frame_at_0m0s_1.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"ilke.iam","content":"<p>Der Autofull M6 Ultra ist mit Abstand der krasseste Gaming Stuhl auf dem MarktSitzheizung, Sitzkühlung und Massagefunktion sorgen dafür das ihr beim Arbeiten und Zocken immer das ultimative Erlebnis habt und durch die Ergonomischen Einstelloptionen habt ihr dabei immernoch eine gesunde und natürliche Haltung<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_yrpd37":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/20251020-152603_-_frame_at_0m23s_1.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Amy Elle","content":"<p>It’s incredibly important to me that he has a supportive but also comfortable gaming chair that looks as cool as his setup will be and did the M6 Ultra deliver! Not only does it have the COOLEST features… 👀 I’m looking at you seat ventilation, buts its lumbar support is so highly adjustable that I knew it would be perfect!<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_gPYmaT":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7_05_webp.webp","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Ryan Mikael","content":"<p>AutoFull M6 Ultra—The Ultimate Gaming Chair is Here! The Best Gaming Chair of 2025! This video provides an in-depth analysis of the AutoFull M6 Ultra to help you make an informed decision. This upgraded model is absolutely worth every penny!From comfort and adjustability to heating, cooling, and massage functions, I'll break down every detail you need to know before purchasing. Whether you're a hardcore gamer or seeking top-tier ergonomic support, the AutoFull M6 Ultra delivers.<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_N39ecC":{"type":"testimonial","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/20251020-164020_-_frame_at_1m17s.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Taylor Jordn","content":"<p>Blend Your Style with Functional Gaming Essentials... Just Like Adding Avocado to a Smoothie!<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}},"testimonial_gbREt9":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7_04_webp.webp","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"","title":"Aidenshow","content":"<p>The AutoFull M6 is like the boss of gaming chairs! Its heating & cooling function, built-in vibration massage, and 6D adjustable armrests create an epic seating experience – great for marathon gaming or getting stuff done.<\/p>","more_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/reviews"}}},"block_order":["testimonial_kw4GmX","testimonial_8DateJ","testimonial_UMkdX4","testimonial_HTwJwH","testimonial_LKtazX","testimonial_yrpd37","testimonial_gPYmaT","testimonial_N39ecC","testimonial_gbREt9"],"custom_css":[".section-header {display: flex; text-align: center; justify-content: center;}"],"name":"Testimonials","settings":{"full_width":true,"stack_t